snippet.title: Falsepine Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Join a long lineage of Hunters as you run and gun through the wild west in this action rogue-like. Take on Bounties, Unlock powerful weapons and come face-to-face with a gallery of terrifying monsters.

Falsepine is available on steam - https://store.steampowered.com/app/2214250/Falsepine/
